   <br>
</dt>
<dd>
   <i>From the announcement: "North Carolina Supreme Court and Court of Appeals opinions are now available on the Internet, direct from the Administrative Office of the Courts.  A visit to the site seems to indicate that, at the moment at least, only 1996 opinions are there."</i>
</dd>

<p>

<dt>
