articles related to those topics.  To subscribe:</i>

<p>

   <i>Send e-mail to: </i>sandy_barnes@journal.com<br>
   <i>With a message identifying yourself and indicating your interest in subscribing to the
Corporate/Securities/Finance Law Abstracts newsletter.</i>

</dd>
