   <b>7.  INTL-DOC, INTERNATIONAL DOCUMENTS DISCUSSION LIST</b>
</dt>
<dd>
   <i>From the announcement: "INTL-DOC, a new listserv for international document librarians and users
of IGO material, has been set up at Northwestern University and is now open to subscribers.  While
INTL-DOC is intended primarily for individuals working with IGO documentation, queries concerning
the literature of foreign national governments and of international affairs in general will be welcomed."
To subscribe:</i>

<p>

<i>Send email to: </i>LISTSERV@LISTSERV.ACNS.NWU.EDU<br>
<i>With message:</i> subscribe INTL-DOC &lt;your first name, your last name&gt;

