Environmental Programme's INFOTERRA Network, UNEP's global information
exchange programme.  Designated as the INFOTERRA Internet node and Regional
Service Centre for Central and Eastern Europe, CEDAR is working with the Austrian
National Focal Point (NFP) at the Austrian Federal Environmental Agency and other
regional and global NFPs to support environmental information dissemination."</i>
