   Welcome to
   <a 
    href="http://www.gwu.edu">
    The George Washington University
   </a>
   <a
    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu">
    Law School
   </a>
   <br>
   Student Intellectual Property Law Association Home Page!
  </p>
  <p>
   The GW Law School Student Intellectual Property Law Association, 
   SIPLA, offers intellectual property, IP, programs geared towards the 
   needs and interests of its members.
  </p>
  <p>
   The GW Law School has the largest number of IP alumni of any law 
   school in the country (currently numbering well over 700).
  </p>
  <p>
   SIPLA works to promote contact between its members and leaders in the  
   IP field, many of whom are GW Law School alumni.
  </p>
  <hr>
  Learn more about the GW Law School SIPLA at the following sites:
