<title>
GWLaw Spring '97 Wait-List Lottery Results
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL" size=-1>
<h5>GW Law School<br>
Records Office</h5><br><P>
<h4>Results From the Wait-List Lotteries<br>
<h5>for November 13, 1996

<br>
<img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" WIDTH=357 HEIGHT=13></h4></h5>


<ul>
<li><b>Winners of a lottery are <i>NOT</i> automatically registered for the course.  Students
who are selected must fill out an add form at the drop/add table in order to enter the
class.</b></li>
<li>For further information about the waitlist lottery system, please see the <a
href="/rec/sp97adrp.htm">Drop/Add Info page</a>.</li>
<p>
</ul>

<ul>
<I>Students listed have been selected by lottery from the following wait-listed courses:</i> 
<li>246-10 Appellate Practice - Michel
<li>262-11 Corporate Law Seminar - Solomon
<li>288-10 Commercial Law Seminar - L.A. Cunningham
<li>352-11 Family Law Seminar - Ross
<li>372-10  Drugs and the Law - Sirulnik / Meyers
<li>395-10  Constitutional Law & the Supreme Court - Garre
<li>399-12 Constitutional Law Seminar - Schaffner
<li>411-10 Health Care Law Seminar - Steele
<li>647-20 Alternative Dispute Resolution - Hoffman
</ul>



