<html>
<head>
<title>
GWLAW Spring '97 Drop/Add Info
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL" size=-1>
<h5>GW Law School<br>
Records Office</h5><br><P>
<h4> Spring 1997 Drop/Add Information<br>
<img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" WIDTH=357 HEIGHT=13></h4>



<ul><dl>
<li>Once students are registered, they are free to adjust their schedules as long as the total
number of credit hours does not exceed 15 credits.  Student can drop/add by submitting a
drop/add form to the Records Office.<br><br>

<li>The deadline for dropping or adding courses is 8pm on Friday, November 15th.  This is the
final day for students to make any adjustments to their Spring 1997 schedules until after the end
of the Fall '96 final exams (December 23, 1996). 

</ul>


<center><p>
<HR size=5 width=50% align=center><p>
<i>The wait list procedure for Spring 1997</i><br><br>
</center>

<ul><dl>
<li>All classes which are closed have wait lists.

<li>Students may not register for a closed class but may sign its waiting list available at
registration.

<li>Should any spaces open in any closed classes, two lotteries will be held to select students.
<br>
<center>----------------</center>

<li>The first lottery will <i>randomly</i> select from the 3L's, 4L's, and LLM students who sign
the wait list at their registration session.

<li>Results of this lottery will be posted on the bulletin board outside the Records Office on
Wednesday, November 6th.  Lottery results will also be posted online at the Records Office's
<a href="/rec/sp97lott.htm">Wait List Lottery Results page</a>.

<li>Students who have been picked must  add the course by filling out a drop/add form.<br>

<center>----------------</center>

<li>A second lottery will randomly select from all 2L students who sign the wait list at their
registration session.

<li>Results of this secont lottery will be posted on the bulletin board outside the Records Office
Wednesday, November 13th.  Lottery results will also be posted online at the Records
Office's <a href="/rec/sp97lott.htm">Wait List Lottery Results page</a>.

<li>Students who have been picked have until 8pm on Friday, November 15th to add the course
by filling out a  drop/add form. This is also the deadline for ALL dropping and adding of classes
until after the end of all the final exams for the Fall 1996 semester (December 23rd).

</dl>
</ul>


<p><br>
<h5><i>Updated: 10/28/96</i><br>

<img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" WIDTH=357 HEIGHT=13></h5>
</font>
<p>

<A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/"><img src="http://128.164.161.15/gwu-logo.gif" WIDTH=50
HEIGHT=50 border=0></A>

<A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/"><img src="http://128.164.161.15/woodicon.gif"
WIDTH=50 HEIGHT=50 border=0></A>


