<html>
<head>
<title>
GWLaw Spring '97 Bump Lists
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL" size=-1>
<h5>GW Law School<br>
Records Office</h5><br><P>
<h4>The Bump Lists
<H5>for November 13, 1996
<br>
<img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" WIDTH=357 HEIGHT=13></h4></h5>

If your name appears on a bump list, you may add any other course as long as it is open and not
on the wait list.  Students may add/drop this week, as well as in January.<br>
<ul>
<i>Students have been bumped (and have already been dropped) from the following courses:</i>
<li>218-11  Professional Responsibility - Jenkins
<li>234-10  Conflict of Laws - Pock
<li>360-11  Criminal Procedure - Butler
<li>364-10  White Collar Crime -  Casino
<li>416-10  Legislation - Block
<li>522-10  International Business Transactions -  Peroni
</ul>

<center><img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" WIDTH=357 HEIGHT=13>
</center>
