<HR size=5 width=50% align=center>

<UL>
         <LI>If any classes oversubscribe due to enrollment caps or room size, students will
be randomly bumped by lottery.  The names of the students who are bumped will be listed here,
and will automatically be dropped from the oversubscribed class.  These students may add any
other class which is open.<br></li><br>
         <LI>The bump lists (if any) will be posted along with the Wait-List Lotteries:<br>
<dd>Any bumps from the 3L's, 4L's, and LL.M. students' registration will be posted
here online, as well as on the bulletin board outside the Records Office, on Wednesday,
November 6, 1996.<br>
         <dd>Any bumps from the 2Ls' registration will be posted here online, as well as on the
bulletin board outside the Records Office, on Wednesday, November 13, 1996.<br><br>


</UL>

