 <head>
  <title>
   The George Washington University Law School Student Intellectual 
   Property Law Association Home Page
  </title>
 </head>
 <body bgcolor="#ffffff">
  <font face="helvetica,arial">
  <hr>
  <h2>
   <center>
    The George Washington University Law School
   </center>
   <center>
    Student Intellectual Property Law Association
   </center>
  </h2>
  <h3>
   <center>
    (SIPLA, founded 1962)
   </center>
   <center>
    720 20th Street, N.W.
   </center>
   <center>
    Washington, DC 20052
   </center>
   <center>
    (202) 293-5585
   </center>
   <center>
    http://www.law.gwu.edu/sipla/
   </center>
  </h3>
  <hr>
  <p>
   Welcome to
   <a 
    href="http://www.gwu.edu">
    The George Washington University
   </a>
   <a
    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu">
    Law School
   </a>
   <br>
   Student Intellectual Property Law Association Home Page!
  </p>
  <p>
   The GW Law School Student Intellectual Property Law Association, 
   SIPLA, offers intellectual property, IP, programs geared towards the 
   needs and interests of its members.
  </p>
  <p>
   The GW Law School has the largest number of IP alumni of any law 
   school in the country (currently numbering well over 700).
  </p>
  <p>
   SIPLA works to promote contact between its members and leaders in the  
   IP field, many of whom are GW Law School alumni.
  </p>
  <hr>
  Learn more about the GW Law School SIPLA at the following sites:
  <ul>
   <li>
    <h2>
     <blink>
      EXTRA!  EXTRA!
     </blink>
    </h2>
    <p>
     Click here to download the recent Hilton Davis U.S. Supreme Court
     Oral Arguments in 
     <a     
      href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/rd/hilton/g/hilton.txt">
      ASCII Text format
     </a>
     .
    </p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     Background
    </h2>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     Feedback
    </h2>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     IP Interests
    </h2>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     <a     
      href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/ip/i/h/spaaipih.html">
      IP Programs
     </a>
    </h2>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     <a     
      href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/of/i/h/spaaofih.html">
      Officers
     </a>
    </h2>
   </li>
   <li>
    <h2>
     <a     
      href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/um/i/h/spaaumih.html">
      Upcoming Meeting
     </a>
    </h2>
   </li>
  </ul>
