  <title>
   GW Law School SIPLA Intellectual Property Programs Home Page
  </title>
 </head>
 <body bgcolor="#ffffff">
  <font face="helvetica,arial">
  <hr>
  <h1>
   <center>
    GW Law School 
   </center>
   <center>
    SIPLA
   </center>
   <center>
    Intellectual Property Programs
   </center>
  </h1>
  <hr>
  <p>
   Welcome to the
   <a 
    href="http://www.gwu.edu">
    GW
   </a>
   <a
    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu">
    Law School
   </a>
   SIPLA Intellectual Property Programs Home Page!
  </p>
  <p>
   The GW Law School SIPLA works to promote contact between its 
   members and leaders in the intellectual property (IP) field, many 
   of whom are GW Law School alumni.
  </p>
  <p>
   SIPLA accomodates the IP interests of its members by sponsoring 
   speakers expert in these and other IP interest areas throughout 
   the year.
  </p>
  <hr>
  <p>
   The GW Law School SIPLA will sponsor
   <a
    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/ip/a/9697/i/h/a9697ih.html">
    1996-1997 IP Programs
   </a>
   .
  </p>
  <p>
   In the past, the GW Law School SIPLA sponsored the following IP Programs:
   <ul>
    <li>
     <h2>
      <a
       href="http://www.law.gwu.edu/stdg/ip/sipla/a/ip/a/9596/i/h/a9596ih.html">
       1995-1996 IP Programs
      </a>
     </h2>
     .
    </li>
   </ul>
  </p>
