  <hr>
  <h1>
   <center>
    GW Law School 
   </center>
   <center>
    SIPLA
   </center>
   <center>
    Committee Meeting 2
   </center> 
  </h1>
  <hr>
  <p>
   Welcome to the
   <a 
    href="http://www.gwu.edu">
    GW
   </a>
   <a
    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu">
    Law School
   </a>
   SIPLA Committee Meeting 2 Page!
  </p>
  <hr>
  <p>
   The GW Law School SIPLA invites you to attend the following
   Committee Meeting:
  </p>
  <dl>
   <dt>
    <h1>
     When & Where
    </h1>
   </dt>
   <dd>
    <p>
     <h2>
      Tuesday, October 8, 1996
     </h2>
    </p>
    <p>
     <h2>
      7:50 PM, in Lerner Room L-201
     </h2>
    </p>
   </dd>
   <dt>
    <h1>
     Topics:
    </h1>
   </dt>
