  <title>

   GW Law School SIPLA 4th Annual Patent Bar Review

  </title>                                          

 </head>                                            

 <body bgcolor="#fff7d6" text="#00295a">            

  <hr>                                              

  <h1>                                              

   <center>                                         

    GW Law School                                  

   </center>                                        

   <center>                                         

    SIPLA                                           

   </center>                                        

   <center>                                         

    4th Annual                                      

   </center>                                        

   <center>                                         

    Patent Bar Review                               

   </center>                                        

  </h1>                                             

  <hr>

  <p>

   Welcome to the

   <a            

    href="http://www.gwu.edu">

    GW                       

   </a>                       

   <a                         

    href="http://www.law.gwu.edu">

    Law School                    

   </a>                           

   SIPLA 4th Annual Patent Bar Review Home Page!

  </p>                                          

  <hr>                                          

  <p>                                           

   The GW Law School SIPLA invites you to attend the following 

   Patent Bar Review:                                           

  </p>                                                          

  <dl>                                                          

   <dt>                                                         

    <h1>                                                        

     Schedule:                                                  

    </h1>

   </dt> 

   <dd>  

    <p>  

     <h3>

      Saturday, February 24, 1996

     </h3>                       

    </p>                         

    <dl>                         

     <dt>                        

      8:30 AM - 12:00 PM         

     </dt>                       

     <dd>                        

      Patent Law basics with an emphasis on the morning session of the 

      Patent Bar Exam

     </dd>           

     <dd>            

      <em>           

       <i>           

        Mike Kaminsky

       </i>          

      </em>          

      , Associate,   

      <i>            

       Finnegan, Henderson, Farabow, Garrett & Dunner, L.L.P.

      </i>                                                   

     </dd>                                                   

    </dl>                                                    

    <dl>                                                     

     <dt>                                                    

      12:00 PM - 1:00 PM                                     

     </dt>                                                   

     <dd>                                                    

      Lunch                                                  

     </dd>

    </dl> 

    <dl>  

     <dt> 

      1:00 PM - 2:00 PM

     </dt>             

     <dd>              

      Claim drafting homework distributed

     </dd>                               

    </dl>                                

    <dl>                                 

     <dt>                                

      2:00 PM - 5:00 PM                  

     </dt>                               

     <dd>                                

      Introductory presentation on claim drafting

     </dd>                                       

     <dd>                                        

      <em>                                       

       <i>                                       

        Dave Hill                                

       </i>                                      

      </em>                                      

      , Partner,                                 

      <i>                                        

       Finnegan, Henderson, Farabow, Garrett & Dunner, L.L.P.

      </i>                                                   

     </dd>                                                   

    </dl>                                                    

   </dd>                                                     

   <dd>                                                      

    <p>                                                      

     <h3>                                                    

      Sunday, February 25, 1996                              

     </h3>

    </p>  

    <dl>  

     <dt> 

      9:00 AM - 12:00 PM

     </dt>              

     <dd>               

      Exam Strategy and tactics, and claim drafting review

     </dd>

     <dd> 

      <em>

       <i>

        David Abraham

       </i>          

      </em>          

      , Student Associate,

      <i>                 

       Finnegan, Henderson, Farabow, Garrett & Dunner, L.L.P.

      </i>                                                   

     </dd>                                                   

