     <dt>                                                    

      12:00 PM - 1:00 PM                                     

     </dt>                                                   

     <dd>                                                    

      Lunch                                                  

     </dd>                                                   

    </dl>                                                    

    <dl>                                                     

     <dt>                                                    

      1:00 PM - 4:00 PM                                      

     </dt>                                                   

     <dd>                                                    

      Small Group Sessions with personalized instruction on claim drafting by

      practicing Intellectual Property Attorneys specializing in your field  

     </dd>                                                                   

    </dl>                                                                    

