<title>
Keuka College: Biochemistry
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff link=0000ff alink=ff0000 vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3><b>Biochemistry</b></font> <br>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font><p>
<font size=+1>
<b>Major Briefs</b><br>
Biochemistry at Keuka College is an interdisciplinary program in the sciences designed for students whose academic interests lie both in the areas of biology and chemistry.

<p>

<b>
Career Options</b><br>
The program provides pre-professional preparation for careers in medicine, dentistry, medical technology, pharmacology, biochemistry, physical therapy, physiology, public health and technical research in a variety of agricultural, genetic and biomedical settings.

<p>
