Keuka College: Extracurricular Opportunities
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff Link=0000ff alink=ff0000 Vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+2>
Natural Science, Mathematics and Physical Education <br></font>
<font size=+3>
Extracurricular Opportunities</font>
<p><font size=+1>

The honorary societies at Keuka College recognize academic excellence and achievement as well as potential for success in specific career fields. Their activities are often instrumental in promoting student interest in particular fields of study. Each society maintains specific criteria for membership. Students who excel in the area of natural sciences can look forward to participation in Chi Beta Phi, a national honorary society for natural sciences, mathematics and psychology. 
