<title>
Keuka College: Education Faculty
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff Link=0000ff alink=ff0000 Vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+2>
Education<br></font>
<font size=+3>
Faculty Profiles</font>
<p>
<font size=+2>Professors</font><p>
<b>Drew J. Arnold</b><br> 
