Professor of Education (1972); B.A., St. John Fisher College; M.A., Ed.D., University of Rochester
<p>
<font size=+2>
Associate Professor</font><p>
<b>Sally C. Wedge</b><br>
Associate Professor of Education (1974); B.A., M.Ed., University of Rochester<p> 
<font sixe=+2>
Assistant Professors</font><p>
