<head>
<title>
Keuka College: Marketing
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff link=0000ff alink=ff0000 vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3><b>Marketing</b></font> <br>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font><p>
<font size=+1>
<b>Major Briefs</b><br>
Keuka's marketing major offers you a wide variety of courses. From Advertising to Retail Marketing to Public Relations, you will acquire the knowledge and skills necessary to be successful in your future career. 
As a marketing major, you'll develop advertising campaigns for radio, TV and print media, conduct research to determine consumer behavior as well as create media kits.
The skills learned in the classroom can be further developed through your participation in various campus activities, including:  the campus radio station, the campus newspaper:  "Keukonian," and the marketing club.
<p>

<b>
Career Options</b><br>
In addition to advertising executives, graduates of Keuka's program can look forward to successful careers in marketing research, advertising, direct marketing, personal selling, public relations, retail management, brand management and organizational buying.
<p>

<b>
<a href="mkcrdr.html">Course Descriptions</a></b><p>

<b><a href="./admifi.html">Admissions Information</a></b></font>
