<html>
<head>
<title>
Keuka College: Management
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff link=0000ff alink=ff0000 vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3><b>Management</b></font> <br>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font><p>
<font size=+1>
<b>Major Briefs</b><br>
The management major is an introduction to all management functions. You may choose to develop special expertise by concentrating in accounting, human resources management, management information systems or marketing.  Our experiencd faculty aim to provide you with the skills that will be needed to make your climb into the "real world" as efficient and successful as possible.
<p>

<b>
Career Options</b><br>
In addition to retail management, graduates of Keuka's program can look forward to successful careers as small business managers, department managers, franchise managers and corporate managers.
<p>

<b>
<a href="mancrdr.html">Course Descriptions</a></b><p>

<b><a href="./admifi.html">Admissions Information</a></b></font>
