<head>
<title>
Keuka College: Spanish and Area Studies
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff link=0000ff alink=ff0000 vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3><b> Spanish and <br>Area Studies</b></font> <br>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font><p>
<font size=+1>
<b>Major Briefs</b><br>
Languages enhance a liberal arts education and are important for careers in government, industry, nursing, social work, education and other fields. Students may be interested in spending a Field Period in a foreign country. Group Field Periods have included travel to Spain, Canada (Quebec), France, Russia, Mexico, Costa Rica and Germany. 
<p>
Keuka offers a minor in Spanish and area studies.


<p>
