Link="0000ff">
<title> Keuka College directories</title>
</head>
<IMAGE align=right SRC="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+2>Keuka College</font><br>
<font size=+3>Directories</font><br>
<BR>
<font size=+2>


<img src="greendot.gif">
<a href="./acad_dir.html">Academic Division</a><br>
