<title>
Lightner Library
</title>
<body background="greenwhi.gif" bgcolor="ffffff" text=000000 link=0000ff vlink=006500>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3>
Lightner <br>Library</font><p><font size=+1>
The Lightner Library is the information center of Keuka. It provides study space for 400 students and has over 95,000 classified volumes. Lightner has a wide variety of electronic resources available including index and full-text databases, access to the campus local area network and the Internet and a new library automated system. Audiovisual facilities are available, and artists exhibit their work in the Lightner Art Gallery.<p>
