<head>
<title>
Keuka College: Career Opportunities
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff Link=0000ff alink=ff0000 Vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3>
Nursing <br></font>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font>
<p><font size=+1>
<b>Career Opportunities</b><br>
The range of career choices for a Keuka nursing graduate is wide! Among the choices are opportunities to work with persons of all ages and backgrounds, be they healthy, ill, injured, disabled or dying. The professional nurse may elect to specialize in such areas as maternity, pediatrics, cancer, rehabilitation, community mental health, public health, school and occupational health and hospice. The professional nurse may work in a variety of rural or urban settings such as hospitals, clinics, home health agencies, schools, urgent care centers or public health departments. Finally, the professional nurse may establish private businesses, providing a unique product line of health services for the public.   

<hr></font><font size=+2>
