<head>
<title>
Keuka College: Fine Arts
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff link=0000ff alink=ff0000 vlink=006000>
<img align=right src="coltop2.gif">
<font size=+3><b>Fine Arts</b></font> <br>
<font size=+2>at Keuka College</font><p>
<font size=+1>
<b>Major Briefs</b><br>
The fine arts-art, dance, music and theater-emphasize the role of creativity in our lives. Course work in art, music, dance and theater gives students the opportunity to explore the varied ways in which individuals express themselves artistically. Courses offer historical and theoretical perspectives, as well as practice in artistic techniques and training in particular disciplines, giving students an appreciation of aesthetics. 
<p>
Keuka offers a minor in art.  
<p>


<b>
<a href="./facrdr.html">Course Descriptions</a></b><p>

