<font size=+2>


Presidential Search Committee Appointed
</font><p>
The Board of Trustees appointed a committee to conduct a search and recommend to the Board
of Trustees a candidate for the presidency of Keuka College. Members of the committee
represent alumni, faculty, students and Trustees. The committee will hold its first meeting this
month with the selection of a search firm its first order of business. The committee anticipates a
large and talented pool of applicants and that its work will be completed by next fall. Members of
the committee include:
