    <li><A HREF="http://ee.tut.fi/laitokset/mit/yleista.html">Measurement and Information Technology</a>
    <LI><A HREF="http://kiila.me.tut.fi/">Production Engineering</A> 
</ul></H4><p>

<H3><a href="http://www.tut.fi/~indeng/">Department of Industrial Engineering and Management</H3></a>
