<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H1>The major functions:</H1></FONT -->
<!-- sisennys tapahtuu DD-tagilla -->
<DD>
<B>-  to provide special services and information for the University's
international students and scholars. Inquiries about admission and
application procedure can be addressed to the International Student Advisor
at the International Office, who provides information for foreign students
wishing to apply for degree  programs or International Programs offered at
TUT.
<P>
- to provide advice and information for students, faculty and staff
interested in study abroad.</B>
