<title>Tampere University of Technology, Department heads </title>
<body>
<h2>TUT, Department heads and Professors,  </h2>



Founded:  1965;<br> 
Language of Instruction:  Finnish<br>
Duration of Academic Year: From the 1st of September to the 31st of May<br>
<hr>
  
Rector:  Prof. Timo Lepistö<br>
Vice-Rector:  Prof. Markku Mattila<br>
Director of Administration:  Seppo Loimio<br>
Director of Computer Centre: 
Director of Extension and Continuing Education Centre,<br>
EDUTECH:  Lasse Grönlund<br>
Director of Language Centre: Danny Donoghue<br>
Director of Digital Media Institute:  Petri Vuorimaa<br>
University Librarian:  Arja-Riitta Haarala<br>
<hr>
<!=====================================================================>

<h3>Department Heads:</h3>

Automation Department: Prof.Pentti Lautala<br>
Dept. of Architecture: Prof. Juhani Katainen<br>
Dept. of Civil Engineering: Prof. Ralf Lindberg<br>
Dept. of Electrical Engineering: Prof. Gunnar Graeffe<br>
Dept. of Environmental Engineering: Prof .Helge Lemmetyinen<br>
Dept. of Information Technology: Prof.  Jaakko Astola<br>
Dept. of Materials Engineering: Prof. Pentti Kettunen<br>
Dept. of Mechanical Engineering: Prof. Asko Riitahuhta<br>
Industrial Engin. and Management: Prof. Erkki Uusi-Rauva<br>
<p>
