<h1>Tampere <br>University of Technology</h1></center>
<p><p>
Welcome to the www-server at Tampere University of Technology!<p>

This server is a part of <a href="http://www.uta.fi/region.html/"> 
<img src="/ttkk.koti/pics/trereg.gif" align="middle" border=0 alt="Tampere Region"></a>
information service.<p>
