<!-- toinen sarake, johon tulee varsinainen leipateksti, leveytta ei ole asetettu -->
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<!-- sisennysta varten tarvitaan DefinitionList -->
<DL>
<!-- uusi kappale aloitetaan P-DT yhdistelmalla -->
<P><DT>
<!-- Otsikoiden fontiksi arial/helvetica, koska se nayttaa paremmalta -->
<!-- Huomaa myos englanninkielelle tyypillinen otsikoiden capitalisointi -->
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H1>Hervanta suburb area</H1></FONT>
</P>
<P><DT>
<DD>
<P>Tampere University of technology is located in the Hervanta suburb
which is about 7km from Tampere downtown. Hervanta was established in
1970's and has now grown to be the biggest suburb in Tampere with a
population of approximately 30000 inhabitants. This quite large
population base guarantees good services in Hervanta, such as several
supermarkets, banks and all other basic conveniences as well as
some special services. The student union of TUT has it's own movie
theatre and disco/restaurant that are like most other services
located in the Hervanta center which is about 0.5km from TUT. To
reach the services not available in Hervanta, there're very good bus
connections to downtown. Several of the dormitories in Tampere are
located very near to TUT.
<P>Hervanta, often also called Herwood, is a growing suburb, and one
of the reasons for this is TUT residing there. Technology Centre
Hermia is located in the immediate vicinity of TUT as well as is VTT,
the Technical Research Centre of Finland. Both have tight connections
with TUT. Another reason might be the nature which is very close as
Hervanta is surrounded by forests.
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H2>Links concerning Hervanta</H2></FONT>
<UL type=disc><UT>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.tut.fi/">TUT homepage</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.hermia.fi/english.html">Technology Centre Hermia</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.uta.fi/maps/hervanta-klik.html">Map of Hervanta</A>
</UL></DL>
<!-- sopivaan valiin voi iskea sinisen viivan erottamaan asioita toisistaan -->
