<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H1>Cafeterias at TUT</H1></FONT>

<!-- sisennys tapahtuu DD-tagilla -->
<DD>

Tampere University of Technology has several cafeterias where a complete hot meal
with bread and beverage for all students costs about FIM 15. University cafeterias are
open Monday through Saturday. Cafeterias are not open during vacations, so weekends and
holidays you will have to prepare your own meals at the appartment.

