<A HREF="info.htm"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnInformationNorm.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Information"></A><BR>
<A HREF="studies.htm"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnStudiesSel.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Studies at TUT"></A><BR>
<A HREF="international.htm"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnInternationalNorm.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Ulkomaille"></A><BR>
<IMG WIDTH=136 HEIGHT=10 SRC="images/BlueLineShort.gif" ALT=""><BR>
<A HREF="http://www.tut.fi/cgi-bin/cgiwrap/~kvweb/aglimpse"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnSearch.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Search"></A><BR>
<A HREF="courseguide.htm"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnCourseGuideNorm.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Course guide"></A><BR>
<A HREF="contact.htm"><IMG WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BtnContactNorm.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Contact information"></A><BR>

</TD>
<!-- toinen sarake, johon tulee varsinainen leipateksti, leveytta ei ole asetettu -->
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<!-- sisennysta varten tarvitaan DefinitionList -->
<DL>
<!-- uusi kappale aloitetaan P-DT yhdistelmalla -->
<P><DT>
<!-- Otsikoiden fontiksi arial/helvetica, koska se nayttaa paremmalta -->
<!-- Huomaa myos englanninkielelle tyypillinen otsikoiden capitalisointi -->

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H1>Structure of Studies</H1></FONT>
<!-- sisennys tapahtuu DD-tagilla -->
<DD>

The degrees to be acquired at Tampere University of Technology are:
<p>
Undergraduate Studies:
<ul type=disc>
<li>Master of Science in Engineering
<li>Master of Science in Architecture
</ul>
<p>
Postgraduate Studies:
<ul type=disc>
<li>Licentiate in Technology
<li>Doctor of Technology
</ul>
<P><DT>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H2>Structure of undergraduate studies</H2></FONT>
<DD>
Students wishing to study at Tampere University of Technology (TUT) for M.Sc. -degrees
must apply for admission to a degree program. There are ten degree programs to choose from.
<p>
Studies are pursued at three levels: general level, subject-related level and advanced
specialized level. General studies (about 2 years) are at the beginning of the studies and
are composed of e.g. mathematics, physics and data processing. General studies in
architecture include courses in arts, social science and mathematics and natural science.
All the courses at general level are given only in Finnish.
<p>
After ca. two years the studies become more subject-related. Students can choose specific
study options within his/her degree program. A Master's thesis is written at the advanced level.
<p>
The degree program of M.Sc. in Engineering requires ca. 6 years and the M.Sc. in
Architec-ture ca. 8 years to be completed.
</DL>

<!-- sopivaan valiin voi iskea sinisen viivan erottamaan asioita toisistaan -->
<IMG WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=14 SRC="images/BlueLine.gif" ALT="- - -"><BR>
<A HREF="studies.htm">
<IMG WIDTH=95 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BackButton.gif" ALT="<- Back" BORDER=0>
</A>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
