one semester. <p>

REQUESTS: Participation on the presentations during one semester. This course is obligatory to
everyone who are going to make their thesis on signal procesing or computer systems.<p>

REQUIREMENTS: Most basic courses should have been passed and most of the advanced
courses should be in execution.<p>

NOTE: This course is recommended to be carried out on fourth year at school and before
beginning your own thesis. Presentations of software systems thesis are also accepted. 80902 and
80903 together replace old course 7900<p>

<p>

