<p>

<p>

<b>83950 Telecommunications Laboratory Course 		7,5 ECTS credits</b><p>

<p>

Lic.Tech. Markku Vanninen<p>

Laboratory exercises 112 h.<p>

Takes place during fall and spring terms.	<p>

<p>

CONTENTS:Measurement of communication circuits and systems. Computer simulation of
communication systems. Experimental work in the area of optical communications.<p>

REQUIREMENTS:Laboratory exercises and reporting the results andwork.<p>

<p>

<p>

<b>83962 Design Project in Telecommunications 		4,5-7,5 ECTS credits</b><p>

<p>

Prof. Petri Jarske<p>

Prof. Markku Renfors<p>

Takes place during fall and spring terms.<p>

<p>

GOAL: Learn project work.<p>

CONTENTS: A project done individually or in group. Reporting the progress in seminars. The credit
units depend on the extent of the project.<p>

REQUIREMENTS: Active participation in seminars, seminar presentations, and accepted project.<p>

NOTES: Mandatory for everybody doing the diploma thesis in telecommunications.<p>

