Modulation methods. Harmonic generation, harmonic elimination and filtering. <p>

REQUIREMENTS: Exam from the contents of lectures and exercises. <p>

LITERATURE: Mohan, Undeland and Robbins, Power Electronics: Converters, Applications and
Design, John Wiley &amp; Sons, Second Edition, 1995.<p>

NOTE: Recommended previous knowledge: 78100, 78110<p>

