<B>20600 Fracture Phenomena and Failure Analysis 4,5 ECTS credits</B><br>
         (only in Finnish)<p>

Prof. Toivo Lepist&ouml;<p>
Lectures 28 h. Exercises 28 h.<p>
Takes place during fall term<p>

