pretreatments, dyeing and finishing of textile products.<p>

REQUIREMENTS: Approved exercises and exam of contents of lectures and
literature.<p>

LITERATURE: To be announced.<p>

<B>30220 Textile Chemistry II	7.5 ECTS credits</B><p>

Prof. Pertti Nousiainen<p>
Exercises 100 h.<p>
Takes place during the both terms<p>

OBJECTIVE: The purpose of this course is to make a student familiar
with one special area of textile chemistry, that are pretreatment
processes, chemistry of dyeing and textile finishing, manufacture of
fibers, the structure and properties of fibers, texturing technology
and manufacture of non-woven.<p>

