methods, Lagrange multipliers, dynamic and geometric programming, search methods. Use of
computer programs in optimization.<p>

REQUIREMENTS: Approved exercises, written examination.<p>

LITERATURE: Stoecker; Design of Thermal Systems, McGraw-Hill. Hillier, Liebermann;
Introduction to Operations Research, McGraw-Hill.<p>

