GOAL: To be acquainted with solid and hazardous waste management, it's targets and tasks.<p>

CONTENTS: Waste management policy and plannig. Administrative and operational aspects.
Classification and composition of wastes. Collection and transportation. Waste minimization,
recycling and reuse. <p>

REQUIREMENTS: Approved exercises and passed written examination.<p>

LITERATURE: Copies of lecture material. Additional reading to be announced at lectures.<p>

<p>

<p>

<b>59411 Physical and Chemical Operations	

      in Solid Waste Disposal 3,0 ECTS credits

</b><p>

Senior Lec. Simo Isoaho<p>

