stabilization. Properties of industrial by-products in earth construction. Ground water in
earthwork. Artificial replenishment of ground water.<p>

REQUIREMENTS: Approved exercises and written examination.<p>

LITERATURE: Lectures.<p>

REMARKS: Preliminary knowledge of the courses 54105 and 54141.<p>

<p>

<b>54192 Engineering-Geological Investigation Methods</b>	<b>3,0 ECTS credits</b><p>

<p>

Associate Prof. Raimo Uusinoka<p>

Lectures 21 h. Laboratory exercises 14h. Planning 8 h.<p>

Takes place during spring term.<p>

