<p>

Prof. Raimo Salokangas<p>

Takes place during fall or spring term. <p>

<p>

GOAL: To focus on a current theme within the field of Construction Economics and Management
and to improve the research and academic writing skills.<p>

CONTENTS: Finnish and international literature on the topic to be focused on. <p>

