<TD>
<DL>
<P><DT>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica">
<H2><A HREF ="http://ee.tut.fi/laitokset/rgi/yleista.html">BIOELECTROMAGNETISM AND  BIOMEDICAL ENGINEERING</A></H2>
</FONT>

The program in Biomedical Engineering  covers a wide range in bioelectromagnetism,
medical instrumentation and modern  physiological signal recording and processing.  The
program gives a solid background both for postgraduate studies and employment in
hospitals, research institutes and industry.<P>

The program is aimed at students having a B.Sc. degree in electrical engineering or
computer science.<P>

The Institute specializes in bioelectric and biomagnetic phenomena, their computer
analysis, modeling and processing.<P>

</DL>
<IMG WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=14 SRC="images/BlueLine.gif" ALT="- - -"><P>
