<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<DL>
<P><DT>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica">
<H2>
<A HREF = "http://sigwww.cs.tut.fi/">DIGITAL SIGNAL PROCESSING</A>
</H2>
</FONT>
The program gives a solid background in modern digital methods, applicable to many
fields of technology, including mobile phones,  biomedical and industrial instrumentation,
digital audio, HDTV and multimedia. Course work centres on signal processing
algorithms, applications and implementations, as well as on laboratory projects using state-
of-the art equipment in signal and videoprocessing and VLSI design.<P>

The Signal Processing Laboratory is one of the largest research groups in the world in its
field and its work is known internationally.<P>
</DL>
<IMG WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=14 SRC="images/BlueLine.gif" ALT="- - -"><P>
<A HREF="osasto1.htm">
<IMG WIDTH=95 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BackButton.gif" ALT="<- Back" BORDER=0>
</A>
</TD>
</TR>
