<!-- Huomaa myos englanninkielelle tyypillinen otsikoiden capitalisointi -->

<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><H1>Orientation</H1></FONT>
<!-- sisennys tapahtuu DD-tagilla -->
<DD>
An orientation course will be held at the end of August.
It will include introductions to the
University and life in Finland. Tours will be
made in the Main University Building, library,
recreational facilities and advisory services.
The course will also include an informal sauna-evening
with other foreign and host Finnish students.
Exact details are given upon each student's arrival.<p>

</DL>
