<!-- uusi kappale aloitetaan P-DT yhdistelmalla -->
<P><DT>
<!-- Otsikoiden fontiksi arial/helvetica, koska se nayttaa paremmalta -->
<!-- Huomaa myos englanninkielelle tyypillinen otsikoiden capitalisointi -->
<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica">
<H1>
Admission Requirements For Postgraduate Studies
</H1>
</FONT>
<!-- sisennys tapahtuu DD-tagilla -->
<DD>
Applicants for licentiate and doctoral studies must be holders of a Master's or equivalent degree in the field which they wish to study. Students with a bachelor's degree are treated as undergraduate applicants.
<DL><DT>
Foreign students wishing to apply to Tampere University of Technology will receive application forms from the International Office of TUT on request. Postgraduate students may apply for admission at any time. The language of Instruction at TUT is Finnish except in the case of very few courses, but postgraduate studies can usually betaken in English (a certificate proficiency in the English language (=TOEFL) is required.Please notice that TUT does not have a TOEFL code number of its own.
</DL>
<p>
<b>No application form available online yet.</b> You can also order application from IO.
<P>
Applications should be sent to:<P>
<DL><DT>
<DD>International Office
<DD>Tampere University of Technology
<DD>P.O.Box 527, 33101 Tampere
<DD>FINLAND</DL>
<P>
Applications will not be processed unless all the following documents are received. Documents can be submitted in Finnish, Swedish or English. All copies and translations must be officially certified as being correct and all translations must be accompanied by a copy of the original. Please, all documents should be sent together and in the same envelope.
<P>
</DL>
<!-- sopivaan valiin voi iskea sinisen viivan erottamaan asioita toisistaan -->
<IMG WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=14 SRC="images/BlueLine.gif" ALT="- - -"><P>
<A HREF="regu.htm">
<IMG WIDTH=95 HEIGHT=35 SRC="images/BackButton.gif" ALT="<- Back" BORDER=0>
</A>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
