<body bgcolor="#ff8888">

<h1>Research of Industrial Management</h1>

<h2>Here is the list of our research projects that are reported in 
English</h2>
<ul>

<li>European Way of Excellence, Quality Demonstration Programme
Case Study Nokia Mobile Phones
<li>Measuring the Stage of Quality Thinking in an Organization
<li><a href="http://www.logistix.fi/prosit.htm">Prosit</a>, Project Supply 
Management Information Technology
<li>Logistics Strategies in Finnish Industry
</ul>
<p>
We do a lot of reseach in other areas, e.g. marketing, productivity,
production, administration, strategy and so on but these are in Finnish.

