<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Dear User!</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>This page has been temporarily taken off line due to its being used for hateful debate, not connected with the subject of this site - the speedy release of Ron Arad.
<P>We apologise to those users who were supportive of our cause through these pages and hope to have the discussion back on-line as soon as possible.
