<HTML>
<HEAD>

<TITLE>Free Ron Arad:  1986-7</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#CC00CC" VLINK="#000066">
<IMG SRC="/Images/head-miss.gif">


<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>1986</H1>
<P>Much has occured since 1986 when Ron fell into captivity.  1986 brought Elie Weisel the Nobel Peace Prize, Imelda and Ferdinand Marcos left the Philippines bringing on the era of Corazon Aquino.  In Eastern Eurpope at Chernobyl nuclear power plant an accident occurred whose effects were felt as far away as Finland. 1986 was also the year in which the Challenger space shuttle exploded killing all seven astronauts, the Iran-Contra affair stole the headlines and U.S. President Ronald Reagan order US planes to bomb the Libyan city of Tripoli.

<P>On October 16 of this year Ron Arad fell into captivity.  Ron hasn't seen his family or friends since.  

<P>
<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>1987</H1>
<P>During 1987 the world heard some South African musicians and singers backing up Paul Simon's on his album Graceland and the Dow Jones broke the 2000 mark and reached 2722 before crashing.  Rashid Karami, premeir of Lebanon, was assassinated and Margaret Thatcher was elected to her third term of office as Prime Minister of Great Britain.  On the Israeli front we saw a rotation of the premiership between Shimon Peres and Yitzchak Shamir and the beginning of a Palestinian uprising, the Intifada.

<P>October 16, 1987 marked Ron's first year in captivity.


