<h1>When You're Home</h1>

When you're home<BR>
Tomorrow, one day soon,<BR>
The sun, the stars, the moon<BR>
will shine so bright.

<P>When you're home<BR>
We'll come and say hello,<BR>
And you will smile and glow<BR>
with all your might.

<p>And if you turn and say,<BR>
Please go, it's been a long day,<BR>
We'll wait a little longer,<BR>
We'll understand,<BR>
We'll sing all night,<BR>
We'll sing and pray,<BR>
Till you say o.k.,<BR>
Until you join us in<BR>
an old forgotten song,<BR>
Da Do Ron Ron....<BR>
