<HTML>
<HEAD>
<!-- Insert title here -->
<TITLE>The Story of Ron Arad (Page 2)</TITLE>
<!-- Enoid of title here -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#CC00CC" VLINK="#000066">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/Images/head-read.gif" ALT="Read Ron's Story">
</CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/Images/young.jpg" HEIGHT=272 WIDTH=220 HSPACE=4 ALIGN=LEFT><P>During 1988, Ron Arad was held by a group called "The Resistance of the Believers" formed by D'orani, which advocated an ideology similar to that of Iran and the Hizballah extremist Shi'ite organization in Lebanon.

<P>D'orani's group, being small and weak, was subject to pressures from various quarters (the Syrians, Amal, and others) concerning the navigator. As a result, in the first half of 1989, D'orani transferred Ron Arad or handed him over to the Iranians in Lebanon.

<P>Ron has been held by the Iranians ever since at an unknown location, probably in Lebanon. The Iranians have never officially admitted that they are holding him, or know his whereabouts.
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
