<DOCNO>WT09-B36-332</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA039-000748-B029-156</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ron-arad.org.il:80/Articles/101.html 194.90.9.24 19970210093229 text/html 2927
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 1997 09:27:57 GMT
