                        (C) The Jerusalem Post 1992
                        Friday, August 23, 1991



Source:


        RED CROSS SAYS IT HASN'T HEARD ARAD IS ALIVE


TEL AVIV - A Red Cross spokesman here said yesterday that his
organization had received no information indicating Israeli airman Ron
Arad is alive.

The announcement contradicts the comment by "an official Lebanese
source" to a news agency in Beirut saying Arad is alive, and that the
Red Cross had been informed of this.



