<DOCHDR>
http://www.ron-arad.org.il:80/Articles/15.html 194.90.9.24 19970210094427 text/html 10185
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 1997 09:39:45 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
